                    <span>If you are interested in quickly learning about how to raise a VC fund, save your time and money. This book does not offer many clues.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Get This Book!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
